index 2db769f..76f4c38 100644
--- a/CHANGES.rst
+++ b/CHANGES.rst
@@ -62,6 +62,11 @@ Unreleased
 -   Contexts created during shell completion are closed properly, fixing
     ``ResourceWarning``s when using ``click.File``. :issue:`2644` :pr:`2800`
     :pr:`2767`
+-   Add ``escape_shell`` parameter to ``click.edit()`` to escape special shell
+    characters in the filename and editor command using ``shlex.quote``,
+    preventing shell command injection when editing untrusted filenames.
+-   Add ``working_dir`` parameter to ``click.edit()`` to set the current
+    working directory of the launched editor process.
 
 
 Version 8.1.8
